title: Zeit Rock Trendy Mountain 11/18: 30 Rock, The Game Awards, Anthony Edwards, Jumpman Logo, Fresh Prince Trailer
itunes:title: Zeit Rock Trendy Mountain 11/18: 30 Rock, The Game Awards, Anthony Edwards, Jumpman Logo, Fresh Prince Trailer
description:
On this edition of Zeit Rock Trendy Mountain Jack and DJ Danl discuss the shitty looking Christmas tree being decorated outside 30 Rock, the Game Awards has released its 2020 nominees, stories about top draft pick potential Anthony Edwards are popping up on social media, a hail-mary catch picture made Nike a bunch of money, and the trailer for the Fresh Prince reunion special has us all weepy!
